            "body": "I'm sorry for the wording, I must admit I was a bit shocked by the experience.\r\n\r\nHowever, stating that my two examples have “objectively(!) maximal contrast” is quite a hyperbole, too. Especially the color contrast between strings and comments in the second example – it is almost zero.\r\n\r\nOf course I use a different colorscheme now, but having such bad contrast would seriously put me off if I were a new user. Of course the defaults are your choice.",
